TI  - A physiographic approach to downscaling fractional snow cover data in mountainous regions
AU  - Walters, Reggie D.
AU  - Watson, Katelyn A.
AU  - Marshall, H.P.
AU  - McNamara, James P.
AU  - Flores, Alejandro N.
